{"id": "1215999113900851310", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1182276243626921984", "author_name": "demaeiccho", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家起点同步才好玩，新手叫没练度玩不了高的，佬叫太简单还念你\n那就都一样，深潜这种东西不应该只是比拼练度凹度，我反正一个界域一队用到死这样", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:26:20.925000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:30:10.107000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
