{"id": "1216002055592738956", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1182276243626921984", "author_name": "demaeiccho", "author_bot": false, "content": "你就算当天出四个拐配队，大家都一样的，难打大家都难打，他能满分你不行，这是为什么呢，还会去把矛盾转移到官方这边吗\n要是别人都满分你不能那我会狠狠嘲笑你", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:38:02.279000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👎", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
