{"id": "1216006309670031411", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1207347087369568268", "author_name": "jpzr2323", "author_bot": false, "content": "那有人死扛一直触发到1%纯纯靠运气摸过去也通关，你也要比一比么", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:54:56.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
