{"id": "1216006734653558804", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1182276243626921984", "author_name": "demaeiccho", "author_bot": false, "content": "现在商店给的造物也不一样啊，通关又不是没有分数评价了，你1%过了自然没有不触发的分高\n排行榜依然存在只不过合并成一个榜单而已", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:56:37.854000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👎", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216007115026731120", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1182276243626921984", "author_name": "demaeiccho", "author_bot": false, "content": "这本身就是个运气游戏，给的造物和死抗完全没问题，现在都是这样为什么锁角色了不可以？", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:58:08.542000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216007554380070992", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前分數比較多 幻夢深潛沒提示 現在是可以了！", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T12:59:53.292000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["392840163732226058"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1215995686286266469", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216040270781485138", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 19, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "那樣的話我覺得這遊戲還可以出一個殘局關卡，\n就像角色試用關一樣，\n每天出一關固定角色固定牌序等隨機種子關卡，\n正確答案要打對順序才能贏的殘局，\n厲害的人可以解謎，躺派可以等佬攻略抄作業，\n其實就是個每日派發獎勵但要寫點功課這樣，\n既體驗自己沒有的角色也可以欣賞官方所設計出來的combo\n新手也能有一個遊戲完全體理想的樣板，可以期待自己成長到那時候\nps1 像這次墨菲試用關一開始就有點難度這樣\nps2 雖然每天要想一個殘局題目出來也不是一件易事\nps3 其實我是想多少窺見一點官方為何認為這隻角色符合設計預期的強度", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T15:09:53.490000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-09T15:20:45.104000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1182276243626921984"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1215996369907486760", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1216057024719360093", "channel_id": "1215696847981781012", "type": 0, "author_id": "1137328302135181312", "author_name": "cra0261_", "author_bot": false, "content": "想問一下6.5倍的關卡裡面，怪物數值實質等於多少的建議等級？75？🤔 \n還是說**怪物實力會依次提高**並不是單純指數值上的提升？", "timestamp": "2024-03-09T16:16:27.940000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-09T16:23:10.809000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215696847981781012", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅關於「幻夢深潛」的再度調整說明", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
